    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Electronic devices that produce oscillatory electrical signals. Commonly used to create sine, square, or sawtooth sound waves for testing purposes or for electronic music.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
